<typeStatus box="[445,555,772,796]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">syntypes</typeStatus>
. Baker deposited this material in his own collection which was later sent to the 
<collectionCode box="[237,326,803,827]" country="USA" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" name="Smithsonian Institution, National Museum of Natural History" pageId="7" pageNumber="6" type="Museum">USNM</collectionCode>
